    verdict:'Claude is the best general-purpose AI for anyone whose work lives in language — long documents, code review, nuanced writing, and analytical reasoning. Its 1M-token context window is practically unmatched for ingesting entire codebases or research corpora in a single session. The free tier (Sonnet 4.6) is among the most capable free tiers of any frontier model.',
