    idealWorkflow:['Index your entire repo on first launch so Cursor has full codebase context from day one','Use Agent Mode (@codebase) for multi-file features: describe the goal and let it plan and edit autonomously','Run Arena Mode when trying a new approach — compare Claude vs GPT-4o output on the same task','Use Background Agents for long-running tasks (test suite generation, large refactors) while you work on something else'],
