    idealWorkflow:['Enable the IDE extension in your existing editor — no setup beyond auth is required','Use inline completions for repetitive code patterns, then Copilot Chat for explaining and refactoring','Assign GitHub Issues to Copilot Coding Agent — it opens a draft PR with the fix for you to review','Use Copilot CLI (`gh copilot suggest`) for shell command help without leaving the terminal'],
