    pitfalls:['Perplexity is a retrieval tool — it can hallucinate when the underlying sources disagree or when it can\'t find good results','Pro search limits (300/day) sound generous but run out fast on intensive research days','Sources are sometimes behind paywalls, making verification difficult without a separate subscription'],
